Yekaterina Aleksandrovna Gamova ( Russian   ; amuru 17 October 1980) bu onye egwuregwu volleyball Russia lara ezumike nka
Ọ bụ onye otu mba nke meriri ihe nrite ọla edo na 2006 na 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, na ihe nrite ọlaọcha na Athens 2004 na Sydney 2000 Olympic Games
N'ihi ogo ya na ikike ya na ụgbụ a, a na-eto ya dị ka "Queen of Volleyball"
Ọ bụ 2.02 m (6 ft 8 in) toro ogologo na nha EU 49 ụkwụ, na-eme ka ọ bụrụ otu n'ime ndị na-eme egwuregwu nwanyị kachasị ogologo n'ụwa   Ọrụ ya bụ n'èzí hitter / n'akụkụ.
Ka ya na Dynamo Moscow na-egwu egwu, ọ meriri nrite ọla ọcha na 2008–09 CEV Indesit Champions League, wee nye ya ihe nrite "Best Scorer"
Maka oge 2009/2010, o sonyeere ndị otu Turkish Fenerbahçe Acıbadem
Ya na ndị otu a meriri Turkish League Championship  wee gaa na 2010 CEV Indesit Champions League Final Four
Ndị otu ya gụchara n'ọkwa nke abụọ ka Volley Bergamo meriri ya wee nye ya "Scorer Best"
Ọ bụ onye otu mba Rọshịa nke meriri asọmpi mba ụwa n'afọ 2010 wee bụrụ onye ọkpụkpọ egwuregwu kacha baa uru
Ka e meriri na nkeji iri na ise nke Brazil na asọmpi Olympic nke afọ 2012, ọ na-eche echiche ịkwụsị iso ndị otu mba na-egwu egwuregwu mana ọ ka na-aga n'ihu n'ọkwa klọb
Amaghị m ma ọ ga-abụ ezumike na-adịgide adịgide, ma ọ bụ na m ga-amaliteghachi mgbe ogologo oge kwụsịtụrụ."

Gamova meriri ya na klọb Russia Dinamo Kazan 2013-14 CEV Champions League nke emere na Baku, Azerbaijan, meriri ndị nwe ụlọ Rabita Baku 3-0 na ọkara ikpeazụ  na 3-0 na Turkish VakıfBank İstanbul na ikpeazụ
Enyere ya onye ọkpụkpọ kacha bara uru na onye kacha nwee ọkaibe
Gamova meriri nrite ọla edo na 2010 FIVB Club World Championship, mgbe otu ya meriri 3-0 na klọb Brazil Molico Osasco maka asọmpi asọmpi
Akpọrọ ya aha Spiker Kachasị Mma na Kachasị Mma n'etiti otu egwuregwu kacha mma
Na May 2016, Gamova kwupụtara na Match TV na na ibe Facebook ya na ọ chọrọ ịla ezumike nká n'ọrụ egwuregwu ya n'ihi mmerụ ahụ
N'ikwu nke ahụ, ọ gaghị eso na Olympic Summer 2016
Mgbe Olympic na London na 17 August 2012, ọ lụrụ onye na-ese ihe nkiri Russia na onye mmepụta Mikhail Mukasei, nwa Svetlana Druzhinina na Anatoly Mukasei
